org.jcvi.jillion.trace.chromat.scf

Interface ScfChromatogramFileVisitor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ChromatogramFileVisitor

    public interface ScfChromatogramFileVisitor
extends ChromatogramFileVisitor
    ScfChromatogramFileVisitor is a ChromatogramFileVisitor that has additional visitXXX methods for SCF specific fields.
    Author:
    dkatzel
